Invocation Name: what animated character am i
des:
Want to know what animated character you would be? Are you a mouse, a duck or perhaps a prince or princess.
Simply ask What Animated Character Am I and we will tell you.
This skill is not an official Disney skill. It has been developed by and for animation fans. It is purely for fun.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
